Creating Week Duration and 12 week. 11

Everything you need is on the zip file for this step.

1- creating  Week Duration

go to power bi desktop and filed like you see on the screenshot.

 right click on created and select or choose to create new column and new window will display paste   the formula for week duration. 

WeekDuration = FORMAT('Incoming_word'[Start of Week].[Date], "M/D/YY") & " " &"-" & " " & FORMAT('Incoming_word'[End of Week].[Date], "M/D/YY")


 do same thing for 12 weeks 


Last 12 Weeks = VAR a = MAX('Incoming_word'[End of Week]) -77

RETURN

IF ('Incoming_word'[End of Week] >= a, "Last 12 Weeks", "Other Weeks")
